						will be expired in
						% if object.expiry_date:
						<strong>${object.expiry_date}</strong>.
						% else:
						<strong>undefined</strong>.
						% endif
						it’s
						% if object.days_left:
						<strong>${object.days_left}</strong>
						% else:
						<strong>undefined</strong>.
						% endif
						days left.
						Please click link below to go to the Blanket Order
